            <title><![CDATA[【老年人如何预防口腔疾病[思考]】老年人由于身体机能衰退，器官功能逐渐降低。口腔的变化也经历了这个自然的过程，尤其是牙齿，牙釉质磨损，牙尖变平，牙龈萎缩...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【老年人如何预防口腔疾病<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】老年人由于身体机能衰退，器官功能逐渐降低。口腔的变化也经历了这个自然的过程，尤其是牙齿，牙釉质磨损，牙尖变平，牙龈萎缩……更容易引发各种牙齿疾病。老年人如何预防口腔疾病，提高生活质量？为了家里老人学起来👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> （中华医学会） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4932771244605490" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">科普中国的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/005ztyuLly1hgqa2fo0evj61f50ssduc02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/ZVC1dyBulx087Fhco1iM01041200Awbz0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691631736&amp;ssig=LLmv0%2F77Ff&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/4xr4Faxklx087FhckIWc01041200iSDa0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691631736&amp;ssig=3Ohra9WpBW&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/88gT4FKglx087FhbXfYs01041200c7xK0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691631736&amp;ssig=5bwdoM5d%2BQ&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4932771244605490&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
